{"tid":512132,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Citra 3DS模擬器討論貼(NDS Desmume後繼機)","createTime":"2017-12-28T07:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T07:20:17.000Z","uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2ca95294b5806d05bd751099a803e190417e2e5f","tid":512132,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T07:20:17.000Z","msg":"當年NDS推出時，Yahoo知識班廢毛一直睇唔起到NDS模擬器，仲嘴串串話唔通滑鼠玩到Touch Mon咩，結果今日因為Desmume，大家可以免費任玩NDS遊戲。今日大家同樣可以免費任玩3DS遊戲，咁當然有任天堂的鎮店之寶：精靈寶可夢啦！(大家買3DS都係想玩佢啫)<br />\n<br />\n係三年前當3DS流行，Switch還未推出時，外國就已經出現各式各樣的「3DS模擬器」，但最後的結果都是悲劇一堆呃人問卷收場....<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/142127_fd56466cce18f18bbf8476f8ade15834.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F142127_fd56466cce18f18bbf8476f8ade15834.png&h=48e7cccd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過多得外國IT狗的努力，真正玩得的3DS Citra終於誕生了<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/142358_3416a51104808e3eb471d756d6d626b9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F142358_3416a51104808e3eb471d756d6d626b9.png&h=b05285a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(點解個logo係個橙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n不過唔緊要，最緊要玩到嘛，立即download落自己E Drive到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/142630_37e599c3a551f21a10ff868c060da164.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F142630_37e599c3a551f21a10ff868c060da164.png&h=aea24276&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(腦內一片空白)<br />\n<br />\n之後就係精靈寶可夢，今次搵藍寶石做測試<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/142908_37e599c3a551f21a10ff868c060da164.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F142908_37e599c3a551f21a10ff868c060da164.png&h=e0e72eb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(搵ROM就自己靠Google大神啦！不過Down Game就快手啦，任豚好小氣架，佢地一見到人地upload開心版就會立即Ban鳩佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n萬事準備好，開始入Game...<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/143338_37e599c3a551f21a10ff868c060da164.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F143338_37e599c3a551f21a10ff868c060da164.png&h=29dfcd4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(無錯你見到的正是始源藍寶石PC版)<br />\n<br />\n揀男定女(唔同GBA版，就算藍寶石主角都係紅色衫)，名字叫Citra，我要比成個九洲居民知我用模擬器支配打機界！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/144816_37e599c3a551f21a10ff868c060da164.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F144816_37e599c3a551f21a10ff868c060da164.png&h=caa738e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/145006_37e599c3a551f21a10ff868c060da164.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F145006_37e599c3a551f21a10ff868c060da164.png&h=14ba3975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這次交時間係自動交跟PC時間，好方便架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/145326_37e599c3a551f21a10ff868c060da164.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F145326_37e599c3a551f21a10ff868c060da164.png&h=448c2de5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n堂堂一位博士比土狼犬追 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/145659_37e599c3a551f21a10ff868c060da164.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F145659_37e599c3a551f21a10ff868c060da164.png&h=cd62f113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前玩GBA版選擇過水躍魚，今次挑戰難度用木守宮打土狼犬<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/151334_37e599c3a551f21a10ff868c060da164.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F151334_37e599c3a551f21a10ff868c060da164.png&h=e5dd47cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然3DS的3D效果同宜家D Steam小品遊戲差不多，但當我地同NDS黑白版比較時...<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/151219_37e599c3a551f21a10ff868c060da164.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F151219_37e599c3a551f21a10ff868c060da164.png&h=e81ffc01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(簡直就係飛躍進步獎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n之後一直向前103路打宿敵(3DS人物會chok樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"}]}